snippet.title: I unsubscribed from Dr. Grande months ago, and now you get why
snippet.description:
In this video, I discuss why I unsubscribed from Dr. Todd Grande and his recent video on Claudia Conway.

Time Stamps:
0:00 Intro
3:56 Red flags I noticed
9:23 Using the title of doctor as authority
13:11 Victim-blaming Claudia Conway
19:58 Questionable sources
20:35 Closing thoughts

Link to my merchandise: https://teespring.com/stores/anas-bazaar

The thoughts expressed in this video are my own personal opinion and do not reflect the opinion of any institution I am involved with.

The contents of this video are for educational and entertainment purposes only. They are not meant to substitute seeking professional therapy.

Please like and subscribe for more real-world applications to psychology! :)
